prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Allow inventory managers and salespersons to log in to the system",
      "evidence_quote": "The system will feature a secure login for salespersons and inventory managers."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Allow inventory managers and salespersons to change their password",
      "evidence_quote": "Change Password: This will allow inventory managers and salespersons to change the password."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Add goods and their corresponding details to the current inventory",
      "evidence_quote": "Add Goods: This will allow adding goods and their corresponding details to the current inventory."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Remove goods from the current inventory",
      "evidence_quote": "Remove Goods: This will allow removing goods from the current inventory."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Place a wholesale order to the supplier",
      "evidence_quote": "Place Order: This will allow placing a wholesale order to the supplier."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Generate an invoice for the order request to the supplier",
      "evidence_quote": "Invoice Generation: This will allow generating an invoice for the order request to the supplier."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Search item details in the current inventory",
      "evidence_quote": "Search Item: This will allow searching the item details in the current inventory."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Generate a bill for the customer selected items from the inventory",
      "evidence_quote": "Receipt Generation: This will generate a bill for the customer selected items from the inventory."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Calculate discount and tax based on the quantity selected by the customer",
      "evidence_quote": "Discount and Tax Generation: This will calculate the discount and tax based on the quantity selected by the customer."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Replace an item in the current inventory",
      "evidence_quote": "Replace Item: This will replace the item in the current inventory."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Cancel a currently generated receipt",
      "evidence_quote": "Cancel Receipt: This will cancel the currently generated receipt."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Update price details of the corresponding item",
      "evidence_quote": "Price Updating: This will update the price details of the corresponding item."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Log an item request from the customer",
      "evidence_quote": "Customer Request: This will log an item request from the customer."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Generate a summary report for all transactions that have taken place",
      "evidence_quote": "View Summary Report: This will generate the summary report for all the transactions that have taken place."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Notify about the removal of goods from the current inventory",
      "evidence_quote": "Expired Goods: This will notify about the removal of goods from the current inventory."
    }
  ]
}

